{"tid":116221,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母有個痴線佬跟撚住我","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T18:09:37.000Z","uid":35034,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd1c57b40103bd26e953b914b73759ff2abf20a","tid":116221,"uid":35034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"啱啱係黃埔等巴士番屋企 有條友企係我後面<br />\n<br />\n我聽緊電話嗰陣條友一腳踩咗落我對鞋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我望住佢 佢笑笑口咁話sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後同我講前面撞車 有排等 問我有無興趣齊搭的士<br />\n<br />\n我睬佢都有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n佢再問我除左巴士有咩去到旺角 我答佢地鐵<br />\n<br />\n佢問地鐵有無樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我答佢話有扶手梯<br />\n<br />\n最後拍我背脊話唔該走咗去<br />\n<br />\n過左陣我發現真係無車  所以去左搭地鐵<br />\n<br />\n行行下見到月台等lift 嗰個位 佢企咗係到 我無理到佢繼續向前行<br />\n<br />\n行行下feel 到有啲奇怪 望向後面發現佢跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻驚到鳩縮衝咗去隔離上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家仲好驚 係咁另轉頭望<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母痴線佬踩花我新鞋 唔屌你係因為講緊電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba06a69bf8249aca71468079eaf8fd66d0b70ae7","tid":116221,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"佢可能以為你跟住佢搭地鐵"},{"pid":"001c539d8f84cbb899e04946a10bb9639fa7cdf7","tid":116221,"uid":35034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:17:03